description: From fore- +‎ take. Also as a back-formation from foretaken. Compare Danish foretage, Swedish företaga.

verbs.description: foretake (third-person singular simple present foretakes, present participle foretaking, simple past foretook, past participle foretaken)

entries.meaning: (transitive) To take, receive, or adopt beforehand; assume.
(transitive) To take or choose before another (option); prefer.
